#----------------------
# CREATE new Owner 
// -> receive POST method on /owners + a Json OwnerRequest obj
#----------------------
###
POST {{baseUrl}}/owners HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

  {
    "name": "eva",
    "email": "eva@woof.net",
    "phone": "111222",
    "address": "bordeaux"
  }

